Package: pkg0
Version: __VERSION__
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 5.0), curl, jq, ca-certificates, openssl
Recommends: cosign
Maintainer: martona <amarton@gmail.com>
Description: sidecar package manager for .debs published on GitHub Releases
 Installs and updates .deb packages straight from GitHub Releases,
 with Sigstore attestation verification via cosign. Invoked separately
 from apt and never touches apt's own inventory; one JSON state file,
 one bash script.
